{"tid":1839002,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人係覺得自己呼吸困難，好似中左招","createTime":"2020-01-24T08:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T03:38:28.000Z","uid":233582,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9ca936c8c1dffface3fe624dabb286cdb85285d8","tid":1839002,"uid":233582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:38:11.000Z","msg":"呼吸個陣心口有少少痛，有陣時吸氣好似吸唔到入個肺到咁，好驚自己中左招"},{"pid":"1777fe5ae347277578b48a7f1afd0326b8e058d1","tid":1839002,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:38:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"e22f459c8d9f46a6c2e177cc84ea70a288d03ced","tid":1839002,"uid":203393,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:40:30.000Z","msg":"自我隔離一下先啦，真係覺得中招馬上call 999, 要救護車送你去醫院，好過自己去周圍傳。<br />\n<br />\n當然如果你想去轉警署報失先都冇問題嘅，畢竟唔見重要野都好大問題"},{"pid":"a0a300a4ecb04c4f1416e6c7b752b546839a7403","tid":1839002,"uid":278168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:40:46.000Z","msg":"深呼吸嗰陣痛我自細不時都有，肋間肌痛，無事。<br />\n一個人緊張嗰陣呼吸過速都會造成唞唔到氣嘅感覺，焦慮症病人經常會遇到呢種情況，放鬆一陣會好返啲。<br />\n<br />\n以上純粹個人經歷，希望你無中招。"},{"pid":"151fd1febcf457f62d5a0fcc449d07116e3dafb2","tid":1839002,"uid":13288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:43:08.000Z","msg":"有啲想吐 唔知關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0325d8504c4e5ae01b108a47d6d29a76277d52","tid":1839002,"uid":154656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:43:52.000Z","msg":"